songs.title: Fvking Pessimist Pt. 3
songs.lyrics:
[Intro]
Aye, 1, 2. Aye aye aye yo aye 1, 2, 3 Bitch!!

[Verse: 1]
Bad life, fast life
You don't have seven
You don't hace five
In my uncle's car
With my demons are
Put the shotgun in my arm

[Verse: 2]
Love me
Hate me
But never forget me
My mind
My time
My life, it's over now
It's time to say... Game over, home'
Dreams are broken
Dreams are stopped
'Cause i'm stupid now
Come come

[Outro]
I keep writing letters for you
Even knowing that you will never read them
I keep listening to our songs
I'm still thinking about you
You will always have a place in my heart
Even if you do not want to be there
Although you are not here anymore
